PLAYER PERSONALITY ARCHETYPES
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- 7 archetypes stored in players.archetype (schema v15):
  normal (35%)       — no effect; baseline majority of roster
  hard_worker (20%)  — +20% chance of extra OVR gain per game (calcDelta bonus)
  coachable (15%)    — +12% chance of extra OVR gain per game (calcDelta bonus)
  team_leader (10%)  — 28% chance per game of +1 chemistry (applyArchetypeModifiers)
  vocal_leader (8%)  — 22% chance per game of +1 chemistry
  selfish (7%)       — 25% chance per game of −1 to −2 chemistry (morale-based)
  troublemaker (5%)  — 30% chance per game of −1 to −2 chemistry (morale-based)
- applyArchetypeModifiers() called automatically inside processGameResult()
  for every team after every simulated game; total swing capped at ±5 per game
- Archetype assigned during generatePlayers() and replenishFAPool(); existing
  players start as 'normal' via DEFAULT
- ChemistryPanel displays ROSTER PERSONALITIES chip row with counts by type
- ArchetypeBadge.tsx: reusable colored badge; renders null for 'normal'
- IPC: get-player-archetype, set-player-archetype (commissioner editing ready)

