GAME SIMULATION ENGINE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- Stats-first scoring: TDs/FGs from team ratings; player stats match scoreboard
- Realistic 18-game schedule: 6 divisional, 8 intra-conf, 4 inter-conf per team
- Team rating pipeline (computeTeamRatings):
  1. Position-weighted base ratings
  2. Morale modifier: effOVR = rating × (1 + (morale − 75) × 0.001)
  3. Coaching modifier: OC/DC +0.15×, HC +0.05× (vs. 70 baseline)
  4. Scheme modifier: roster fit bonus/penalty
  5. Chemistry modifier: −4 to +3 based on team_chemistry value
- GamePlanOptions: optional offense/defense mode passed to simulateGame();
  read from settings key gameplan_{season}_{week}; applied as rating multipliers:
  Offense modes: balanced (default), spread (+pass −run), power_run (+run −pass),
  west_coast (+short pass efficiency), play_action (+play action bonus)
  Defense modes: base (default), blitz (+pass rush −coverage), zone_coverage
  (+coverage −rush D), press (+man coverage), prevent (+deep coverage −rush)
- Game script: trailing teams pass more; leading teams run more
- Overtime: TD wins outright; FG gives opponent a chance; no ties
- Weather: clear / rain / snow / wind with pass, rush, score multipliers
- Home field advantage: +0.5 scoring drives; away QB accuracy penalty
- Depth chart integration: healthy players cascade to backups
- Background simulation: simulateGame runs in a worker thread (simWorker)

SEASON ADVANCE (advanceSeason in SeasonService.ts)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 1. Age all non-retired players
 2. Progression / regression by dev trait + age bracket
 3. Breakout bonuses for standout season performers (age ≤ 28)
 4. Practice squad development (age ≤ 23, up to +3 OVR)
 5. Dev trait evolution
 6. Retirement (age/OVR thresholds, chance-based)
 7. Morale update (win%, contract year, playing time)
 8. Open free agency (CPU GM cuts + resign + contract expiry)
 9. Contract demand news events (elite players, final year)
10. Injury + waiver cleanup
11. Archive season stats to career_stats_history (with team_id)
12. Prune raw stats (DELETE WHERE season < current − 1)
13. Prune news events (keeps 3 seasons)
14. HOF inductions for newly retired players
15. Season award news events (MVP, DPOY)
16. Evaluate owner goals + update patience
17. Advance season counter
18. Replenish FA pool

IN-SEASON PLAYER PROGRESSION (ProgressionService.ts)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- Runs after every simulated game
- gradePerformance(): 0–100 grade by position from game stats
- calcDelta(): OVR delta from grade + age modifier + dev trait bonus +
  archetype bonus (hard_worker +20% / coachable +12% extra gain chance) +
  OVR ceiling dampening + OVR floor protection
- Breakout news events on 2+ OVR gain or young standout

